/-- Composing the preadditive yoneda embedding with the forgetful functor yields the regular
Yoneda embedding.
-/
@[simp]
theorem whiskering_preadditive_yoneda :
    «expr ⋙ » preadditiveYoneda
        ((whiskeringRight («expr ᵒᵖ» C) AddCommGroupCat (Type v)).obj (forget AddCommGroupCat)) =
      yoneda :=
  rfl
